project.name: The Environmental Defense Initiative
project.description:
TEDI is an international youth-led group dedicated to raising environmental awareness and providing a platform for those looking to create an impact.
Our website is filled with broadly applicable technologies such as a custom blog publishing system, petition tracker, user management for access to toolkits, and emailing solutions. Because of this, we open-sourced our code and built it to be easily adaptable for any other nonprofit organization to use.
